{"tid":1459544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大件事都冇人提既？","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:00:21.000Z","uid":81488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8983b1a3f8b0a8bf682275dae187e8959f0ff658","tid":1459544,"uid":81488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呃左大家入黎..<br />\n<br />\n之前塞左咁多次得到D咩？<br />\n唔係話影響民意，係影響民生比影響政府大得多。可能少少一個勤工獎無左，就少左一千幾百既眾籌同物資，所以我一直都唔太讚成做。<br />\n就算各有各做大家都要食腦，我唔係叫你地唔好做，但都想比意見大家諗下，係呢個時候塞鐵係咪有用？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機場就唔同啦，大大減少市民既抱怨，<br />\n而影響力係大到上國際層面。</span><br />\n就算影響唔到航班，大家都要保持溫度，<br />\n直至818大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n不割席</span>"},{"pid":"c7e359c1e36a358fbb90c21a9f7934872a14a815","tid":1459544,"uid":81488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f96af01492d4f3dda3d6641f074d65fbcb8008b","tid":1459544,"uid":81488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"33967d250e84660f79757e7ff3a8a5271b17c7f7","tid":1459544,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459505/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459505/page/1</a><br />\n由得警方御用暴徒自己衝防線<br />\n入得機場請保持克制<br />\n和理非可以睇表演如何鎮壓、如何自編自導<br />\n<br />\n下次唔洗再問去定留 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f310UGJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff310UGJ.jpg&h=61673d36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee5c6c9349dd75d248176e0ca25f3bb03437d0b5","tid":1459544,"uid":81488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"